1.CHECK YOUR SYSTEM
______________________________________________________________________________
Be sure your system is Raspbian Stretch (some  RsP is Raspbian Jessie)
Do 
$  sudo nano /etc/apt/sources.list
replace the Jessie with Stretch
... another will be write latter



2.INSTALL CAFFE (this will take 5~6 hours )
_______________________________________________________________________________
flowing this guide https://github.com/leo2105/Caffe-installation-Raspberry-Pi-3

pay attention to the protobuf install,just ignored that,use 

$ pip install protobuf

